        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container
                .masthead-subheading It's been a long road
                .masthead-heading.text-uppercase The story of a Bootcamp
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase.js-scroll-trigger(href='#services') GO AHEAD

        // Services
        section#services.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase STACK
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted there's no jedi warrior without them lightsaber
                .row.text-center
                    .col-md-3
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            img(src='assets/img/stack/nodejs.png', alt='')
                        h4.my-3 nodeJS
                        p.text-muted
                            | Fast and reliable backend performance, amazingly simple and powerful.
                    .col-md-3
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            img(src='assets/img/stack/express.png', alt='')
                        h4.my-3 Express.js
                        p.text-muted
                            | The perfect framework for smooth and fresh backend node development.
                    .col-md-3
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            img(src='assets/img/stack/mongodb.png', alt='')
                        h4.my-3 MongoDB
                        p.text-muted
                            | Super fast and secure db. What else?
                    .col-md-3
                        span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                            img(src='assets/img/stack/react.png', alt='')
                        h4.my-3 React
                        p.text-muted
                            | and redux, and soon recoil. Frontending like a boss.

        // About
        section#about.page-section
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Project timeline:
                    p.section-subheading.text-muted A humble review of the jobs made so far.
                ul.timeline
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/1.jpg', alt='')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 Web foundaments
                                h4.subheading HTML / CSS
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | the challenge: building a video streaming service mock using only self-developed html and css. No libraries or frameworks allowed. Not even the slightiesst Js.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/2.jpg', alt='.')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 intro Js - advanced frontend
                                h4.subheading vanilla icecream.
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | Managing the DOM 'like a boss' simply with vanilla. Also, using preprocessors like SASS and bundling with webpack.
                    li
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/3.jpg', alt='')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 node | backend 
                                h4.subheading The MEN from MERN
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | Building an API rest from scratch using expressjs and mongodb. Securized with JWT and serving the bakend of the anunciaLOL app.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/4.jpg', alt='')
                        .timeline-panel
                            .timeline-heading
                                h4 REACT
                                h4.subheading enjoying web components
                            .timeline-body
                                p.text-muted
                                    | using classes, hooks, redux, router, context and soon to come recoil. Frontending like a pro.
                    li.timeline-inverted
                        .timeline-image
                            h4
                                | Best stuff
                                br
                                | is yet
                                br
                                | to come!

        // Team
        section#team.page-section.bg-light
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase About myself
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted the boss.
                .row
                    .col-lg-4
